               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols. 5ra-121va)&#xD;
I-1) Homily by Athanasius [Timothy], Patriarch of Alexandria for the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols. 5ra-13rb); miracle (fols. 13rb-15ra); commemorative notice (fols. 15ra-17rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 17rb)&#xD;
I-2) Homily by an anonymous author for Tāḫśāś (fols. 17va-24rb); miracle (fols. 24rb-26va);  commemorative notice (fols. 25va-26rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 26rb) &#xD;
I-3) Homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for Ṭǝrr (fols. 26va-37rb); miracle (fols. 37rb-38rb); commemorative notice (fol. 38rb-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 38va-vb) &#xD;
I-4) Homily by an anonymous author for Yakkātit (fols. 38vb-42va); miracle (fols. 42va-43vb); commemorative notice (fol. 44ra-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 44va-vb) &#xD;
I-5) Homily by [Severus], Metropolitan [Patriarch] of Antiochia for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 45ra-63va); miracle (fols. 63va-65ra); commemorative notice (fol. 65ra-rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 65rb-va) &#xD;
I-6) Homily by [Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs the Orthodox] for Miyāzyā (fols. 65va-70vb); miracle (fols. 70vb-73ra); commemorative notice (fol. 73ra-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 73va-vb) &#xD;
I-7) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Ethiopia for Gǝnbot (fols. 73vb-75ra); miracle (fols. 75vb-76vb, 87ra-va); commemorative notice (fols. 87va-88ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 88ra) &#xD;
I-8) Homily by [Yoḥannǝs], Metropolitan of ʾAksum for [Sane] (fol. 88rb-94vb, 77ra-vb); miracle (fols. 77vb-79ra); commemorative notice (fols. 79ra-86va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 86va-vb) &#xD;
I-9) Homily [by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] for Ḥamle (fols. 95ra-100rb); miracle (fols. 100rb-101rb); commemorative notice (fol. 101rb-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 101vb) &#xD;
I-10) Homily by an anonymous author for Naḥāse (fols. 102ra-105vb); miracle (fols. 105vb-106vb); commemorative notice (fols. 106vb-107ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 107ra-rb) &#xD;
I-11) Homily by an anonymous author for Maskaram (fols. 108ra-111ra); miracle (fols. 111rb-113vb)&#xD;
I-12) Homily by an anonymous author for Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 114ra-118va); miracle (fols. 118va-120vb); commemorative notice (fols. 120vb-121va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 121va) &#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-3.</summary>
